Penny Cook https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Penny_Cook 0 Penny Cook (born 13 July 1957) is a multi Logie Award-winning Australian actress and writer. She graduated from the National Institute of Dramatic Art (NIDA) in 1978, she has been active in television and film, best known of her soap opera roles as Vicky Dean Bowen in A Country Practice And Dr. Elly Fielding in E Street, as well as appearing in stage roles Penny_Cook ( born 13_July_1957 ) is a_multi_Logie_Award-winning_Australian_actress_and_writer .
